Best, tt, best.
Best, tt, best.

141
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:21,120
Time, tt, time.
Time, tt, time.

142
00:12:21,780 --> 00:12:28,040
Do, dd.
Do, dd.

143
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:30,600
Do.
Do.

144
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:34,040
Odd, dd.
Odd, dd.

145
00:12:35,820 --> 00:12:38,176
Odd.
Odd.

146
